    <body>
        <p>A global dictionary is a file that contains words and can be used for spell checking by any <MadCap:variable name="Other.Product" /><MadCap:conditionalText MadCap:conditions="Products.Flare,Products.Lingo,Products.Mimic"> project</MadCap:conditionalText><MadCap:conditionalText MadCap:conditions="Products.Contributor"> file</MadCap:conditionalText> you open on your computer. <MadCap:conditionalText MadCap:conditions="Products.Flare,Products.Lingo,Products.Mimic">This is a convenient way to ensure that all of your projects are using the same spellings for terms, rather than having each project rely on a different dictionary.</MadCap:conditionalText></p>
